1)Given an email is sent to "roadside-ch@sixt.com"
2)Then a case must be created via email-to-case with the From address in the email composer 
set as roadside-at@sixt.com where the Subject and Body is "Roadside tire issue.Please send help"
3) Verify if the Case classification contains Case Reason, Case sub-reason and Case subsub reason
4) If it is blank even after 2mins Case Owner must be "DACH_RSA_During_Support"
5) Verify that the Case priority must be High
6) Verify the default language has to be "German"
7) Verify the default POS has to be "Switzerland"
8) Go to the "Feed" and click on "Write an Email" to check the email signature